Document: ColorRect
Path: godot/classes/class_colorrect.rst
Summary: Displays a solid-colored rectangle with an option to use Panel for borders.

Displays a rectangle filled with a solid color. If you need to display the border alone, consider using a Panel instead. The color property determines the fill color of the rectangle. For border-only visualization, Panel is recommended as an alternative.
